~/.mozilla/firefox/<your-profile>/chrome/userChrome.css

How to find your profile - 
https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/profiles-where-firefox-stores-user-data

You need to make sure that on the about:config page in Firefox, 
the toolkit.legacyUserProfileCustomizations.stylesheets preference is set to true and then restart the browser. 


Scrollbar setting

Open about:config
Search "scrollbar"

layout.testing.overlay-scrollbars.always-visible = true
widget.non-native-theme.gtk.scrollbar.round-thumb = false
widget.non-native-theme.gtk.scrollbar.thumb-size = 1
